step 1:
command: bluetoothctl

step 2:
put AirPods in Pairing mode: press and hold the setup button on the back of the case until the status light flashes white

step 3:
inside bluetoothctl CLI, 
command: scan on

step 4:
wait for your airpods to appear in the list of available devices.
note the MAC address of your airpods.

step 5:
enter below for initiating pairing,
command: pair <MAC address>

step 6:
command: connect <MAC address>

step 7:
exit bluetoothctl,
command: exit

